  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a chat user, I want to always see the names of people where that have added me as a contact so that I know who I'm talking to.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFrom a users point of view the app seems to sometimes forget names of contacts and relationship. This tends to happen with multi-devices or across installs.\r\n\r\nOne day I'll see I'm chatting with \"Fred\", and the next day I see \"random three names\".\r\n\r\nI'll also see the \"add to contacts\" UI of someone I've added multiple times already\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n- Remember the name and connection status\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n- Random names showing along with \"add to contact\" UI\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n\r\n",
